    89	    neutralized_at_b_lo)` — i.e. **True iff the enriched arm is not held back by an *unremoved* length-norm
    90	    penalty.** Mechanical, reproducible, pooled (per-class reported), pre-registered `b` (no argmax), and
    91	    **isolated to length** (uses placebo = pure length), **distinct from criterion 1** (enriched vs placebo).
    92	    Same fixed-seed bootstrap helper.
    93	- **Power guard (codex concern #4) — separate 15b tolerance, NOT external ε:** the external near-parity
    94	  band ε=0.05 is for FathomDB−Mem0; the internal D2 lever uses its **own pinned lift-of-interest
    95	  `δ_d2 = 0.03`** (the smallest enriched−placebo recall lift that would justify a schema migration). If
    96	  the 15b paired MDE for enriched−placebo `> δ_d2`, the verdict is **INCONCLUSIVE** (not FAIL).
